description: Spectacular mixed-use building in the very heart of South Boston's Andrew Square. This turnkey property contains four residential apartments and two separate ground-level commercial spaces. The apartments consist of two three-bedroom units and two two-bedroom units, all of which are currently leased. The two commercial spaces are also leased to longtime tenants. Nearly every inch of this building, both inside and out, has been updated over the past five to ten years. Directly across the street from the Andrew Sq Station, this property provides opportunities for both current income and future possibilities.
